  "body": "Currently we only bundle and publish the truffle cli w/ a `package.json`. This is because there is only a `package.json` in `packages/truffle`. See #2555 for the possible security issues with this current setup.\r\n\r\nWe should probably generate a `package-lock`, convert it into a `shrinkwrap`, & proceed with publishing the truffle cli with a shrinkwrap. (Recommended for global cli installations [which is how we recommend users to install & use truffle]).",
